 The wedding took place in Westville, KwaZulu-Natal.The bride had a total of two wardrobe changes, consisting of colourful and vibrant African prints. The couple are the proud parents of a baby girl Khai.Kwesta features his family in his latest music video for the song Ngiyaz'fela Ngawe."To the father of my child, my partner, my best friend &amp; my husband. You are one in a million. Thank you for choosing me, thank you for bringing together our families, thank you for being the greatest dad ever, thank you for being so loving. I love you homie, let's do this forever thing," Mvelase wrote on Instagram after the wedding.